WEBVTT

00:12:28.894 --> 00:12:31.735
that we all take for granted
at this point,

00:12:31.759 --> 00:12:36.298
but which was against the law
and against protocol for African Americans

00:12:36.322 --> 00:12:39.196
at the time that she would have been
growing up in the South,

00:12:39.220 --> 00:12:40.402
had they stayed.

00:12:40.426 --> 00:12:43.037
And that is just to walk into a library

00:12:43.061 --> 00:12:45.156
and take out a library book.

00:12:45.180 --> 00:12:49.156
Merely by making
the single decision to leave,

00:12:49.180 --> 00:12:53.219
her parents assured that their daughter
would get access to books.

00:12:53.727 --> 00:12:56.465
And if you're going to become
a Nobel laureate,

00:12:56.489 --> 00:12:58.433
it helps to get a book now and then.

00:12:58.457 --> 00:12:59.724
You know, it helps.